OL,4,G1230FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GDeborah and Wayne host at their
OL,6,     GB&B, Braddon Hall, in Torquay.
OL,7,     GBut there are concerns over
OL,8,     Gsqueaky beds and mismatched
OL,9,     Gtypefaces, and allegations fly
OL,10,     Gduring an archery competition.
